quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  91,1,De sun its brightness
  91,2,moon subsequentis it
  91,3,Feria reveals
  91,4,Nox covers
  91,5,Caelum Eum built it
  91,6,Terra Eum sustains it
  91,7,Anima Eum created it
  91,8,Tunc showed it quod est malus quod est bonus
  91,9,Successful est unus redeems it
  91,10,Failing est unus neglects it
  91,11,Thamoud's disbelief causa them transgress
  91,12,They subsequentis malus among them
  91,13,Deus messenger dictus to them Hoc est deus camel; let eam drink
  91,14,They disbelieved eum slaughtered eam! Their Dominus tunc requited them pro their sin annihilated them
  91,15,autem those qui advenit post them remain heedless